name: SeattleRaces
0:
”Alexa Open Seattle Races”
”Alexa ask Seattle Races about today”
”Alexa ask Seattle Races about this week”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: seattle races
des:
"Alexa, open Seattle Races". 

 Seattle Races responds: You can search for all races, or 5K, 10K, half-marathons or marathons.

You say "5K" 
 Seattle Races responds: You can search for today, this week, next week, this month, next month, or a specific date.

You say "Today"
 Seattle Races responds with list of races found for today or, if none today, those races coming up next.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
